    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you aren't a doctor but i'm just trying to make sense of it. basal is for background stuff right? if i barely ate anything, wouldn't there be less glucose in my system for the insulin to deal with? i just dont want to crash in the middle of the night.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
